# Backend Rules

## Clean Architecture

- Controller → Service → Repository (strict separation)
- Controller: HTTP concerns only (parse, call service, respond)
- Service: business logic dan orchestration antar repo
- Repository: SQL queries only, parameterized input, soft delete (`deleted_at`)

## TypeScript

- Strict mode aktif — tidak ada `any` type
- Definisikan return type untuk semua function
- Gunakan interface/type untuk request/response data

## Input Validation

- Semua input divalidasi dengan Zod di controller layer
- Throw AppError jika validasi gagal
- Jangan assume frontend validation

## Error Handling

- Throw AppError (dari `src/lib/errors.ts`) dari service/repository
- Centralized error handler middleware catch dan format response
- Error response: RFC 7807 format (`{ success: false, error: { code, message, details } }`)
- Jangan expose stack trace di production

## Testing

- Service layer wajib unit test (Vitest)
- Happy path dan error case coverage

